Vol / Page: 3
Edition:
Quote: .. I was there when a piece of wood, about two foot long, such as they use for foundation piles or blocks [sic]; I said to the girl, where did you get the piece of wood from; she made no reply; I said to the girl, where did you get the piece of wood from; she made no reply; I said that piece of wood belongs to Mr. R. Davies, and it cost the man 6d. or 1s., and it is a shame that it should be burnt when he wants it for his building ...
